Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧  聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:13.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一名身份不明三十五歲左右的男子被卡車撞倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,現已失去意識  並且大量出血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:13.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:14.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那已經沒救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,另外卡車司機安全無事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說起來  我被卡車…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:31.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,同樣被撞到的兩名高中生  目前下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,正在進行搜尋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請求緊急支援  Over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那三個人得救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很重啊  小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  畢竟連飯都是敲地板讓人送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,連續宅在家二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你知道這裡是哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真吵  不用那麼大聲我也聽得見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:06.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,血壓過低
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,準備輸血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:13.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,聽得到嗎  知道自己的名字嗎  能說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我要死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過也好  反正我的人生也已經沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:25.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過至少想要童貞畢業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好耀眼  我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  這傢伙是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這麼輕易就把我這超100公斤重的漢子抱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼人啊  不要啊  好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啥啊  真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  臉那麼紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,奶子好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說的哪國語言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,話說這是哪  不是醫院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這傢伙在幹什麼啊  我可是重傷員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過這個人真漂亮啊  歐美人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼沒防備的話  我就要摸胸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.76,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看來是我轉生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒想到這種做夢一般的事竟然會變成現實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保羅和塞妮絲  年齡大概二十歲出頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,從34歲的我看來  說是年輕人也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,年紀輕輕就造孩子  真讓人嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過能免費吸美女的奶子真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然因為對方是母親  完全興奮不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪烏斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的名字大概是叫魯迪烏斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,過了半年  也能理解一點語言了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,因為年齡還很小  記性異常地好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,女僕莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,擁有很棒的胸器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不可以一個人到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這不是拿來戴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:04:00.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,塞妮絲大人  恕我直言  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪烏斯大人是不是被什麼髒東西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.76,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼啊  含糊不清的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小孩子嘛  把內褲套在頭上也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真是美麗的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,總感覺我看過這裡的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,果然是在歐洲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:34.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然而這裡也太偏遠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大概這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那邊就拜託你了  莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,電和煤氣都沒有  這是什麼時代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,既然都轉生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我還是想玩玩電腦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:46.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:04:59.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,頭被撞到的時候  不要亂動它比較好哦  這位夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,居然這都不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:19.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以防萬一  給你施加個讓痛痛飛走的咒語吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,神聖之力如芳醇之食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這就是這個國家的「痛痛快飛走」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:37.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}賜予失去力量之人再次站起來的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,繼父親之後母親也是中二病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是戰士和僧侶結婚了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.28,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Healing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  不痛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,別看媽媽我這樣  以前可是冒險者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  我聽見好大一聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,親愛的  魯迪摔下來撞到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷靜點啊  小孩子就是會經常跌倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}而且就算受傷  你來治好他不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,莫非這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可是要是受了重傷我治不好怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:17.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  已經可以斷定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這裡不是地球  而是別的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,劍與魔法的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,腰腿也變得結實了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:45.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這不是連猴子聽到都會為之興奮的單詞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真想快點自己試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖說如此  現在的我能做到的事情並不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:23.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,家裡只有五本書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是這個世界的書很昂貴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,還是因為保羅他們不怎麼讀書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對有上千本書的我來說真是難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然全都是輕小說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:40.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,讀不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,首先還是要搞懂這邊的文字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,又過了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:52.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然只有五本  有時候保羅也會讀給我聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我在一定程度上能讀懂文字了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:08:00.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是  那個老爸很是質疑幼兒能否理解書裡的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  我對這本書很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法課本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有些內容彷彿前世也在哪裡看到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:13.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,例如  魔法有詠唱和魔法陣兩種發動方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但現在的主流是詠唱  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好像有各種各樣的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,而且  讓我在意的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,書上寫著  每個人魔力的總量在生下來時就基本固定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感覺自己的遺傳因子會沒什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過總而言之先試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:43.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,給予你所求之處以水之加護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,清涼細流在此顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.59,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Ｗater Ball
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,水球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼不飛出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,和格鬥遊戲的連擊練習一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,集中精神  不斷在腦海中想像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然後試著實際操作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我還沒進行詠唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我的MP就這麼點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,睏了的話要好好上了廁所再到床上睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,都這個年紀還被誤會尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可惡  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,經過一段時間的嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我搞懂很多事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那本書居然騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔力的總量會隨著使用而增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不用詠唱也可以使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是把要寫的東西都列舉出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是這麼輕易就能做到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,詠唱還有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,莫非詠唱是使魔法自動化的原理條件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不用次次都集中精神去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要出聲就能完成一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是這樣的話  好處就很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,首先第一點  方便傳授
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,詠唱的話就能一次成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也許是在傳授過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:11.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,逐漸變成「詠唱是必不可缺的」這種說法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,第二點  方便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,攻擊魔法是在戰鬥中使用的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,比起閉上眼睛使勁地集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,快速詠唱才會更迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪  差不多該睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,親愛的  我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,還沒行呢  好戲現在才開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}親愛的~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,為什麼魔力總量會增加還是個謎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也許是進行鍛鍊的結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算經過努力鍛鍊  魔力總量也會有上限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  現在下結論還為時尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  比如說可能會隨著成長而增加之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:54.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,幼兒期使用魔力的話  上限會飛躍性地增加之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保不齊是唯獨我才有的特殊體質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,如果剛剛的假設沒錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要做的事情就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在成長期結束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,盡最大可能地去鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是  這個怎麼才能射出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,做到了  做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,終於搞清楚吟唱的原理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這個魔法是按照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,「生成-設定大小-設定彈速-發射」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這個流程來完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,應該是這樣沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,之前是因為我沒有設定彈速才沒有射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感覺魔力總量也增加得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,試試中級魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,優柔的水精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,流淌大地之上溪流之王女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以汝蘊藏之強力  沖潰世間萬物吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.54,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Splash Flow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,激流衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:01.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是魔物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但這附近不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,難道你開口念了這本書上面的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,難道說會魔法的小孩很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,會被送去接受異端審問之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不要  不要火刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,親愛的  你聽見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們家的孩子果然是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但這可是中級的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,現在就雇個魔法教師過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是在那之前  我還沒教過他識字…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,將來肯定是個很厲害的魔法師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:52.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我們不是約定過是男孩就培養成劍士嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是這個年紀就會使用中級魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,約定就是約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼約定  親愛的總是不遵守約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的事和這是兩碼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,上午學魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,下午練劍不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,親愛的  在孩子面前吵架不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,於是乎我們家就僱傭了一個家庭教師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然一直在家裡耍劍  看起來很閒的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保羅姑且還算是名騎士  負責管理這個村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,托這個福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,因此為我這個小孩找個老師並不困難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但怎麼說這也是國家邊境上的偏遠鄉村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然擔心過會不會有人應聘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,結果很快就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,根據父母的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,來的人估計是已經隱退的冒險者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:46.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,作為魔法師研究多年魔法的中年人或者老人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,長滿白須的  一看就知道是魔法師的那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,之前是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是洛琪希·米格路迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,別說鬍子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,來了個好像連那裡的毛都沒長齊的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,年紀差不多是個初中生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:08.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,蘿莉的身形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:08.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,藐視的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷淡的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,集齊三個屬性  簡直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請務必嫁給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就是那個來當家庭教師的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這還真是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好小隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不想被你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,自卑感嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在說胸部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以我要教的學生在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啊  就是這個孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,偶爾會有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過是稍微長大了點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就以為孩子有魔法天份的笨蛋父母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,聽到了  洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}又撲了個空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但我並不認為這個小孩能理解魔法的理論
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒問題  我家魯迪很優秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我會盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在外面教嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這不是肯定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法大致可以分成三類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,攻擊魔法  治癒魔法  召喚魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:24.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,分別有初級  中級  上級  聖級  王級  帝級  神級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一共這七個等級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然後使用魔法就需要魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要麼使用體內的魔力或…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,行吧  總之我現在示範一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你試著模仿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,需要詠唱的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,給予你所求之處以水之加護
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,清涼細流在此顯現
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.18,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Ｗater Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,水球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:14.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那棵樹是我媽媽精心種植的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,神聖之力如芳醇之食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:26.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,賜予失去力量之人再次站起來的力量吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.37,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Healing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,哦  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你還會治癒魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  中級以下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,厲害  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  只要認真練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這種程度誰都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看起來這傢伙真容易攻略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼請做一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:47.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法教科書裡沒有任何關於無詠唱的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,雖然是在無意間使了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,其實是否觸犯了什麼禁忌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希也說過需要詠唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼目前還是使用詠唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說不定這很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,給予你所求之處以水之加護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你剛剛縮略詠唱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平時都是縮略的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平時都是無詠唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,無詠唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平時都是無詠唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:37.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看來很有培養價值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,請不要把我們家的樹當實驗品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一上來就犯錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,明天就是解僱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老師對不起  都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,快二十年沒和人說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不知道這時應該說什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  快想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是說過很多次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,色情遊戲的主人公在這時會說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老師剛剛沒有失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是積累了經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:47.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,話說回來  洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:52.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,進屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,先讓我們互相介紹下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:57.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:03.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但我沒什麼能作為回報的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好了  快進屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魯迪也快來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:18.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那麼我們就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小洛琪希的歡迎會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,彷彿在做夢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,被卡車撞上瀕死的我在做的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不過就算是這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:41.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在這個世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也應該可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,像人一樣去生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,像人一樣去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,遇上挫折也能再爬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,依舊繼續前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算是這樣的我  也應該可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,沒有工作  家裡蹲  廢物一般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也能夠重新開始人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,認真地活下去
